{"tid":1807673,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《黃色經濟利是》開始籌備農曆新年「和你封」！","createTime":"2020-01-02T02:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T11:24:32.000Z","uid":172454,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"421eba4da615ca8f47e962b7bbe88c7a876a1a1f","tid":1807673,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"咁多位，月尾就係農曆新年，雖然革命尚未成功，但利是始終要封。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年唔好再封現金，改為封黃色經濟代用券！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錢始終都要出，不如放落黃色經濟圈，等收利是既人不論黃藍變相都要加入。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首選光時禮品卡，歡迎大家留言提供其它選擇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkongs.com/collections/%E7%A6%AE%E5%93%81%E5%8D%A1/products/100-li-pin-qia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkongs.com%2Fcollections%2F%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%258D%25A1%2Fproducts%2F100-li-pin-qia&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOACPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=2bc03b5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkongs.com/collections/%E7%A6%AE%E5%93%81%E5%8D%A1/products/100-li-pin-qia</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0251/7840/6989/products/GiftCard_100_360x.png?v=1570116274\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0251%2F7840%2F6989%2Fproducts%2FGiftCard_100_360x.png%3Fv%3D1570116274&h=3fa4fecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不過佢得個禮品卡號，可能要自己印個卡號出黎封。</span><br />\n<br />\n另外亦可以將「恭喜發財」依句咁支那人貪錢特質既說話改為「光復香港」！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講冇利是！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d6d8b80007d3c127934a4327acf30abf138b67","tid":1807673,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:59:11.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"343dcc3014ebc237c6de12f0ecd058962edba72f